# Spotify Clone API - Phase 6 Tests (File Upload & Advanced Features)
# Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ===== FILE UPLOAD TESTS =====

### Upload user avatar (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/avatar.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload artist image (admin - replace TOKEN and ARTIST_ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/artist/ARTIST_ID_HERE/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="artist.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/artist.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

