### ===== FILE SERVING TESTS =====

### Serve uploaded image file
GET http://localhost:3000/api/upload/serve/images/FILENAME_HERE.jpg

### Serve uploaded audio file
GET http://localhost:3000/api/upload/serve/audio/FILENAME_HERE.mp3

### Get file information (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/upload/info/images/FILENAME_HERE.jpg
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### ===== PERFORMANCE & MONITORING =====

### Performance health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health/performance

### Cache statistics (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cache/stats

### Clear specific cache type (admin - requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cache/clear
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "type": "search"
}

### Clear all cache (admin - requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cache/clear
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{}

### ===== API DOCUMENTATION =====

### View Swagger API Documentation
GET http://localhost:3000/api-docs

### Get OpenAPI JSON spec
GET http://localhost:3000/api-docs/swagger.json

### ===== ERROR HANDLING TESTS =====

### Upload without file (should return error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/avatar
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Upload invalid file type (should return error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/document.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload oversized file (should return error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="large-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/large-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Try to access non-existent file
GET http://localhost:3000/api/upload/serve/images/non-existent-file.jpg

### Upload without authentication (should return error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
