### ===== INTEGRATION TESTS =====

### Search with caching (should show X-Cache header)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Đen&limit=5

### Search same query again (should hit cache)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Đen&limit=5

### Get trending searches with caching
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/trending?limit=5

### Get trending again (should hit cache)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/trending?limit=5

### Artist details with caching
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists/ARTIST_ID_HERE

### Artist details again (should hit cache)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists/ARTIST_ID_HERE

